@startuml
scale 1400 width
title VBoxManage clipboard serve - source / format event path
hide empty description
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam dpi 96

[*] --> Setup : serve starts
Setup : Get IClipboard and IHostClipboard
Setup : Register event listener
Setup --> ServeLoop
Setup --> Failed : setup error

state ServeLoop {
  [*] --> Waiting
  Waiting : Common wait state
  Waiting : waits for event, timeout or signal
  Waiting --> Stopping : timeout or signal
  Waiting --> Dispatch : event received

  Dispatch : Decode VBoxEventType
  Dispatch --> SourceFormatEvent : SourceChanged or FormatChanged
  Dispatch --> OtherEvent : DataChanged, DataRequested,\nTransfer, Error or ModeChanged

  SourceFormatEvent : Inspect event source
  SourceFormatEvent --> ReadCurrentFormats : SourceChanged and source == Guest
  SourceFormatEvent --> UseEventFormats : FormatChanged and source == Guest
  SourceFormatEvent --> Continue : source != Guest

  ReadCurrentFormats : IClipboard::ReadFormats()
  ReadCurrentFormats --> FilterFormats : read succeeded
  ReadCurrentFormats --> Continue : no formats or read failure

  UseEventFormats : Use formats carried by the event
  UseEventFormats --> FilterFormats

  FilterFormats : Keep formats serve can read back
  FilterFormats : Drop unsupported MIME types
  FilterFormats : Drop self-induced guest format echo
  FilterFormats --> ReportGuestFormats : supported and not suppressed
  FilterFormats --> Continue : unsupported or self echo

  ReportGuestFormats : IHostClipboard::ReportFormats(Copy, Guest, formats)
  ReportGuestFormats --> RememberEcho : success
  ReportGuestFormats --> FailedEvent : COM error

  RememberEcho : Remember reported MIME list
  RememberEcho : Suppress next matching guest echo
  RememberEcho --> Continue

  OtherEvent : Handled by another focused diagram
  OtherEvent --> Continue

  Continue --> Waiting
  FailedEvent : Print serve failure
  FailedEvent --> Stopping
}

ServeLoop --> Cleanup : stopped
Failed --> Cleanup
Cleanup : IHostClipboard::Clear()
Cleanup : Unregister listener
Cleanup : Uninstall signal handler
Cleanup --> [*]

note right of ReportGuestFormats
  Main ReportFormats path:
  - validates action, Guest source, mode and MIME types
  - maps MIME types to SHCLFORMATS
  - updates the advertised Guest format state
  - calls GuestShCl::reportFormatsToHost()

  This makes guest-owned formats visible on the
  native host clipboard without copying payload bytes.
end note

@enduml
' EOF
